# Django devartis admin


## Install

```
pip install django-devartis-admin
```

## Configuration


Add devartis-admin before contrib.admin and
make sure you have sites app installed and you added a SITE_ID on your settings

```
INSTALLED_APPS = (
    'devartis_admin',
    'django.contrib.admin',
    # ...
    'django.contrib.sites',
    # ...
)

SITE_ID = 1
```
